window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>You can listen to this comforting story for free on your device with the Audible Stories Skill. Just say “Alexa, read me a family story,” or “Alexa, read me a story” to hear more free genres.</b></p> <p>In a far off land, a very musical king has a not-very-musical son. Everyone pretends to enjoy the prince’s terrible concerts, but a bold servant girl refuses to play along. The king demands she be punished, but the prince shows mercy. Happily, the prince and the servant girl come up with an arrangement that showcases the prince’s true talent.</p>"; 
